<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div>Pathological Diagnosis :</div><div>Ovary, __, frozen biopsy: </div><div>Stromal tumor, with differential diagnoses of fibroma or</div><div>thecoma.</div><div><br/></div><div>NOTE: Extensive sampling is needed to exclude malignant component. Please follow the pathology report of the subsequent permanent specimen for a definitive diagnosis.</div><div><br/></div><div>Gross description:</div><div>The specimen consists of a piece of ovarian tumor measuring _ cm and _ gm. The fallopian tube measures __ cm (length x diameter).</div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div></en-note>      ]]>
    </content>
  </note>
  <note>
    <title>Gestational endometrium with Arias-Stella reaction</title>
    <created>20180105T013504Z</created>
    <updated>20230606T080712Z</updated>
    <note-attributes>
      <author>Elaine huang</author>
      <source>desktop.win</source>
      <source-application>evernote.win32</source-application>
    </note-attributes>
    <content>
      <![CDATA[<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?>
<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div>gestational endometrium with Arias-Stella reaction.</div><div><br/></div><div><span style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">Microscopic description:</span></div><div><span style="font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">Only decidual tissues with hypersecretory glands </span><span style="line-height: 1.45;">exhibiting Arias-Stella phenomenon are seen. No </span><span style="line-height: 1.45;">villous tissue, trophoblasts or fetal products are </span>identifiable.     </div><div><br/></div><div>These findings are also noted in missed abortion and in ectopic pregnancies. Please correlate.</div><div><br/></div></en-note>      ]]>
    </content>
  </note>
  <note>
    <title>Gestational tissue</title>
    <created>20170725T065159Z</created>
    <updated>20170725T065210Z</updated>
    <note-attributes>
      <author>Elaine huang</author>
      <source>desktop.win</source>
      <source-application>evernote.win32</source-application>
    </note-attributes>
    <content>
      <![CDATA[<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?>
<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div>Sections show gestational tissue with discernible trophoblasts and chorionic villi as well as blood clot tissue and inflammatory exudates.</div></en-note>      ]]>
    </content>
  </note>
  <note>
    <title>Gestational tissue, c/w incomplete abortion</title>
