<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div>PATHOLOGIC DIAGNOSIS:</div><div>Uterus, content, therapeutic D &amp; C ---</div><div>Gestational tissue, consistent with incomplete abortion.</div><div><br/></div><div>Gross description:</div><div>The specimen consists of multiple pieces of tissue measuring __ gm in total.</div><div><br/></div><div>All for section.</div><div><br/></div><div>Microscopic description:</div><div>Sections show blood clots tissue admixed with decidual tissue and presence of chorionic villi and trophoblasts.</div><div><br/></div></en-note>      ]]>
    </content>
  </note>
  <note>
