      <![CDATA[<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?>
<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div>Glandular and stromal breakdown</div><div><br/></div><div>Microscopic description:</div><div>Section reveals mainly blood clots with some fragmented clusters of endometrial glands and condensed cluster of stromal cells. No frank malignancy is noted.</div><div><br/></div></en-note>      ]]>
    </content>
  </note>
