  <note>
    <title>未命名記事</title>
    <created>20180531T031015Z</created>
    <updated>20240306T080805Z</updated>
    <note-attributes>
      <author>Elaine huang</author>
      <source>desktop.win</source>
      <source-application>evernote.win32</source-application>
    </note-attributes>
    <content>
      <![CDATA[<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?>
<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div>High-grade squamous intraepithelial lesion (HSIL) (CIN2)</div><div><br/></div><div>Microscopic description:</div><div>The cervical tissue shows conspicuous maturation but prominent parabasal atypia including variation in nuclear size, hyperchromasia and presence of mitotic figures. </div><div><br/></div><div>It is also demonstrated by positive immunostaining for p16 and</div><div>increased Ki-67 labeling index in the dysplastic cells. </div><div><br/></div></en-note>      ]]>
    </content>
  </note>
