<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div>Leiomyoma.</div><div><br/></div><div>MICROSCOPIC DESCRIPTION:</div><div>Sections show bland-looking spindle-shaped cells arranged in interlacing fascicles with focal degenerative change.</div></en-note>      ]]>
