    <updated>20230830T082726Z</updated>
    <note-attributes>
      <author>Elaine huang</author>
    </note-attributes>
    <content>
      <![CDATA[<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?>
<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div>Leiomyoma with infarct-type necrosis.</div><div><br/></div><div>MICROSCOPIC DESCRIPTION:</div><div>Sections show bland-looking spindle-shaped cells arranged in</div><div>interlacing fascicles with focal infarct-type necrosis.</div><div>Neither overt cellular atypia nor significantly increased mitotic activity is noted.</div></en-note>      ]]>
