<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div>chronic inflammation, with no ectocervical tissue present for evaluation.</div><div><br/></div><div>Microscopic description:</div><div>Section shows endocervical tissue only with scattered</div><div>lymphocytic infiltration. There is no ectocervical or</div><div>transitional zone tissue present for evaluation.</div></en-note>      ]]>
