  <note>
    <title>NOTE Cx 上皮不完整</title>
    <created>20181231T070319Z</created>
    <updated>20190704T015359Z</updated>
    <note-attributes>
      <author>Elaine huang</author>
      <source>desktop.win</source>
      <source-application>evernote.win32</source-application>
    </note-attributes>
    <content>
      <![CDATA[<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?>
<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div><br/></div><div>NOTE: The dysplastic epithelium is focally attenuated without surface epithelium for evaluation of degree of dysplasia. Follow-up or re-biopsy is suggested.</div><div><br/></div><div><br/></div><div>The fragmentation of dysplastic cells leads to difficulty of evaluation of degree of dysplasia. And the dysplastic cells are exhausted out in further sections for p16 and Ki-67 immunohistochemical analysis. HSIL cannot be excluded.</div><div><br/></div><div>Observation with a repeat biopsy is suggested.</div></en-note>      ]]>
    </content>
  </note>
  <note>
    <title>未命名記事</title>
